
Command format:

calipso                            : Show this help file.

calipso site <name>                : Create site in folder.
calipso install                    : Ensure valid installation.

calipso cluster server.port=3000   : Run as cluster.
calipso server server.port=3000    : Run as a single server.

calipso modules list               : List installed modules.
calipso modules install *mod@ver   : Install module@version, or reinstall module.
calipso modules check              : Check installation of all modules.
calipso modules enable *mod        : Check installation of one/all modules.
calipso modules disable *mod       : Check installation of one/all modules.

calipso test                       : Run all tests.

calipso script help *<name>        : This help script, optional script name. 
calipso script <name> *params      : Run a script with <name>, with params.

